prompts.frontCover: A charming and humorous watercolor illustration of a slightly frazzled, but very happy, cartoon sloth wearing a party hat, hanging upside down from a tree branch. The sloth is enthusiastically, yet very slowly, attempting to blow out a single, large, lit candle on a cupcake that is balanced precariously on its belly. Colorful confetti is gently drifting down around the scene. Centered on the card, in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script, is the text "happy birthday". The entire design is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges.
